<zk>
<label multiline="true">
When using inplace editing with combobox, clicking on the drop-down button 3 times cause the combobox to loose its "editing" state and revert to "label" state.

1 - click the combobox, toggle to the editing state and open popup.
2 - click the combobox again, close popup
3 - click the combobox again, popup should reopen.
</label>
					<combobox value="default value" inplace="true">
						<comboitem>one</comboitem>
						<comboitem>two</comboitem>
						<comboitem>three</comboitem>
					</combobox>
</zk>